\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 A hunter asking for help in hauling a magnificent kill to his camp would be told, \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8216\'91you think this skinny bag of bones is worth carrying?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 If one wants to be well thought of, he will be generious. If he strays from this ideal, he will be reminded of it with humor. If he persists in not sharing - he will be actively disliked.}
