\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Several of the world\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s great monotheistic religions preserve, largely unaltered, the ultimate sacred propositions of aramaic speaking societies that lived too long ago. }
